#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.120"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.120:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.120:0.2"
msgid "12. Āpāyikavagga"
msgstr "12. Bound for Loss"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.120:0.3"
msgid "120. Paṭhamasoceyyasutta"
msgstr "120. Purity (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.120:1.1"
msgid "“Tīṇimāni, bhikkhave, soceyyāni."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these three kinds of purity."

msgctxt "an3.120:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni tīṇi?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.120:1.3"
msgid "Kāyasoceyyaṃ, vacīsoceyyaṃ, manosoceyyaṃ."
msgstr "Purity of body, speech, and mind."

msgctxt "an3.120:1.4"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, kāyasoceyyaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is purity of body?"

msgctxt "an3.120:1.5"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti, adinnādānā paṭivirato "
"hoti, kāmesumicchācārā paṭivirato hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s when someone doesn’t kill living creatures, steal, or commit sexual "
"misconduct."

msgctxt "an3.120:1.6"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, kāyasoceyyaṃ."
msgstr "This is called ‘purity of body’."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.120:2.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, vacīsoceyyaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is purity of speech?"

msgctxt "an3.120:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco musāvādā paṭivirato hoti, pisuṇāya vācāya paṭivirato "
"hoti, pharusāya vācāya paṭivirato hoti, samphappalāpā paṭivirato hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s when someone doesn’t use speech that’s false, divisive, harsh, or "
"nonsensical."

msgctxt "an3.120:2.3"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, vacīsoceyyaṃ."
msgstr "This is called ‘purity of speech’."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.272"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an3.120:3.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, manosoceyyaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is purity of mind?"

msgctxt "an3.120:3.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco anabhijjhālu hoti abyāpannacitto sammādiṭṭhiko."
msgstr "It’s when someone is content, kind-hearted, and has right view."

msgctxt "an3.120:3.3"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, manosoceyyaṃ."
msgstr "This is called ‘purity of mind’."

msgctxt "an3.120:3.4"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, tīṇi soceyyānī”ti."
msgstr "These are the three kinds of purity.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.120:3.5"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
